Metadata: Sea Grant College Program 1979-1981 Program Report (Oregon)
program reports (annual, progress, planning reports, etc)

An Oregon State University / Oregon Sea Grant College Program report for 1979-1981. Article topics include: Study aids shrimp industry; The Office of Management and Budget (OMB) wants to see Sea Grant eliminated; Sea Grant's Future - Is it a Dream?; Hey, What's A Sea Grant?; Is there Oil in Oregon's Future?; Estuary Table set for super supper; Mammal film wins Outdoor Writer's award; Computer plan could save ports millions; Bridge-eating gribbles found; Volume fishing; Aquaculture team visits Zaire; Squid for supper; Mussels tasty protein source; Scientists raise reef and predict new fishery; Netarts; Record chum run. A program status report and budget summary for 1979-1981 is also included.
